{"tid":1843152,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"與醫護同行 全港大罷工公投","createTime":"2020-01-26T05:35:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-26T17:03:56.000Z","uid":118276,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3551ab63230b15cf77deec25faf3ce302dcebf51","tid":1843152,"uid":118276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T05:35:21.000Z","msg":"醫護罷工計劃正式出爐！非醫護人員既你，又支唔支持全港大罷工，與醫護同行？<br />\n<br />\n首先，你要<ins>download左個App先投到票</ins>！<br />\n香港地投票 ~ 下載連結：iOS / Android<br />\n<a href=\"https://hkvote.org/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkvote.org%2F&d=1bJdDSIrk6tBa%2BBM68SGev2x0mEA6i1FZlyL0j1bjmE%3D&h=cfd209d7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hkvote.org/</a><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>你支唔支持全港大罷工，以支援香港醫護？<br />\nA: 支持<br />\nB: 不支持<br />\nC: 沒意見<br />\nD: 不確定</strong><br />\n<br />\n投票傳送門：<a href=\"https://hkvote.org/Topic.php?id=1033\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkvote.org%2FTopic.php%3Fid%3D1033&d=1bJdDSIrk6tBa%2BBM68SGev2x0mEA6i1FZlyL0j1bjmE%3D&h=8f781489\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hkvote.org/Topic.php?id=1033</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>24小時投票結果會正式去信各大工會</strong></span></div><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />參考Post<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家支唔支持醫護大罷工？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1842456\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1842456</a><br />\n<br />\n(突發)醫管局工會罷工計劃正式出爐，促請醫管局回應訴求<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1842943/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1842943/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n此投票App與google form/tg polling最大不同之處：<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: green;\">4大特點</span></strong></span></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">1）投票資料多重加密及數據存放於外國 身分保密<br />\n2）只限香港境內進入投票 謝絕五毛<br />\n3）多項措施盡力確保一人一票 提高投票公信力<br />\n4）毋須輸入個人資料 下載app後可在不同議題投票 方便易用</div><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">投票時需暫停使用VPN</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望大家幫手去facebook WhatsApp分享，每人分享俾5個人<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />自己香港自己救<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"47946318a0e8b904c5cae739c86c1472fb43398b","tid":1843152,"uid":126621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T05:40:01.000Z","msg":"都就死 仲返乜野工"},{"pid":"c